<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>태양광 모니터링 - 기술 소식</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.10.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/lib/animate/animate.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Heebo', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .navbar {
            background-color: #6a11cb;
            padding: 15px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            margin: 0 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .navbar .team-name {
            position: absolute;
            left: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .right-nav {
            position: absolute;
            right: 20px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logout-btn {
            margin-left: 15px;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border: 2px solid #17a2b8; /* 민트색 테두리 */
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background-color: #6a11cb; /* 네비게이션 바 색상 */
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .logout-btn:hover {
            background-color: #5c0db6; /* 마우스 오버 시 약간 더 어두운 색 */
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }
        .news-section h2 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .news-section ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .news-section ul li {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .news-section ul li a {
            color: #333;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar" style="position: relative;">
        <div class="team-name">ANS</div>
        <a href="/dashboard">발전량 통계</a>
        <a href="/forecast">발전량 예측</a>
        <a href="/mode">모드</a>
        <a href="/trade">전력 거래</a>
        <a href="/news">기술 소식</a>
    
        <div class="right-nav">
            <span><%= userNickname %>님 환영합니다!</span>
            <a href="/user/logout" class="logout-btn">로그아웃</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    

    <div class="container">
        <div class="news-section">
            <h2>최신 태양광 기술 소식</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.newsfreezone.co.kr/news/articleView.html?idxno=584286" target="_blank">대전시, 2024 글로벌태양광학술대회 개최</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.solarpowerworldonline.com/2024/02/gamechange-solar-increasing-annual-us-manufacturing-capacity/" target="_blank">GameChange Solar increasing annual US manufacturing to 35 GW</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.pv-tech.org/global-solar-tracker-installations-to-reach-752gw-between-2024-and-2030/" target="_blank">Global solar tracker installations to reach 752GW between 2024 and 2030</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.betanews.net/article/1464937" target="_blank">현대차 미국 조지아 공장 태양광전력으로 가동…태양광발전 시장 관심 고조</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.pv-tech.org/soltecs-new-floating-solar-tracker-draws-on-naval-design-principles/" target="_blank">A new concept in floating solar trackers</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/renewables/indias-remarkable-journey-towards-energy-transition/articleshow/107694363.cms" target="_blank">India's remarkable journey towards energy transition</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
